batchLiquidations(uint256[]).details: Function to liquidate multiple loans in batch.

params.tokenIds: - list of tokenIds of loans to liquidate

returns.refund: - amounts from collateral tokens being refunded to liquidator
returns.totalLoanLiquidity: - total loan liquidity liquidated (after write down)

borrowLiquidity(uint256,uint256).details: Borrow liquidity from the CFMM and add it to the debt and collateral of loan identified by tokenId

params.lpTokens: - quantity of CFMM LP tokens requested to short

returns.amounts: - reserves quantities withdrawn from CFMM that correspond to the LP tokens shorted, now used as collateral
returns.liquidityBorrowed: - liquidity amount that has been borrowed

cfmm().details: cfmm - address of CFMM this GammaPool is for

returns.tokenId: - unique id of loan struct created

decreaseCollateral(uint256,uint256[],add.details: Withdraw collateral from loan identified by tokenId

params.amounts: - amounts of collateral tokens requested to withdraw
params.to: - destination address of receiver of collateral withdrawn

returns.tokensHeld: - updated collateral token amounts backing loan

depositNoPull(address).details: Deposit CFMM LP token and get GS LP token, without doing a transferFrom transaction. Must have sent CFMM LP token first

params.to: - address of receiver of GS LP token

returns.shares: - quantity of GS LP tokens received for CFMM LP tokens

depositReserves(address,uint256[],uint25.details: Deposit reserve token quantities to CFMM (instead of CFMM LP tokens) to get CFMM LP tokens, store them in GammaPool and receive GS LP tokens

params.amountsDesired: - desired amounts of reserve tokens to deposit
params.amountsMin: - minimum amounts of reserve tokens to deposit
params.to: - address of receiver of GS LP tokens

returns.reserves: - quantity of actual reserve tokens deposited in CFMM
returns.shares: - quantity of GS LP tokens received for reserve tokens deposited

factory().details: factory - address of factory contract that instantiated this GammaPool

getCFMMBalances().details: Balances in CFMM at last update of GammaPool

returns.cfmmInvariant: - total liquidity invariant of CFMM last time GammaPool was updated
returns.cfmmReserves: - total reserve tokens in CFMM last time GammaPool was updated
returns.cfmmTotalSupply: - total CFMM LP tokens in existence last time GammaPool was updated

returns.data: - struct containing all relevant global state variables that are not updated from time passage or accrued trading fees

returns._0: lastPrice - calculates and gets current price at CFMM

returns.cfmmInvariant: - latest total invariant in the CFMM
returns.cfmmReserves: - latest token reserves in the CFMM
returns.cfmmTotalSupply: - latest total supply of LP tokens in CFMM

returns.cfmmReserves: - latest token reserves in the CFMM

getLatestPoolData().details: Returns additional nonzero fields (e.g. lastPrice, borrowRate, etc.)

returns.data: - struct containing all relevant global state variables and descriptive information of GammaPool. Used to avoid making multiple calls

getLatestRates().details: Get latest rate information from GammaPool

returns.data: - RateData struct containing latest rate information

returns._0: loanCount - total number of loans opened

getLoans(uint256,uint256).details: Get list of loans and their corresponding tokenIds created in GammaPool. Capped at s.tokenIds.length.

params.end: - end index of array wishing to get tokenIds. If end > s.tokenIds.length, end is s.tokenIds.length
params.start: - index from where to start getting tokenIds from array

returns._loans: - list of loans created in GammaPool

getPoolBalances().details: Balances in the GammaPool of collateral tokens, CFMM LP tokens, and invariant amounts at last update

returns.borrowedInvariant: - invariant amount borrowed from GammaPool including accrued interest, maps to lpTokenBorrowedPlusInterest
returns.lpInvariant: - invariant of CFMM LP tokens in GammaPool not borrowed, maps to lpTokenBalance
returns.lpTokenBalance: - CFMM LP token balance of GammaPool
returns.lpTokenBorrowed: - CFMM LP token principal amounts borrowed from GammaPool
returns.lpTokenBorrowedPlusInterest: - CFMM LP token amounts borrowed from GammaPool including accrued interest
returns.tokenBalances: - balances of collateral tokens in GammaPool

returns.data: - struct containing all relevant global state variables and descriptive information of GammaPool. Used to avoid making multiple calls

getRates().details: Interest rate information in GammaPool at last update

returns.accFeeIndex: - total accrued interest in GammaPool at last update
returns.lastCFMMFeeIndex: - total accrued CFMM fee since last update

getRebalanceDeltas(uint256).details: Get rebalancing quantity to be able to fully close loan

returns.deltas: - collateral amounts being bought or sold (>0 buy, <0 sell), index matches tokensHeld[] index. Only n-1 tokens can be traded

returns._decimals: - array of decimals of ERC20 tokens of CFMM
returns._names: - array of names of ERC20 tokens of CFMM
returns._symbols: - array of symbols of ERC20 tokens of CFMM
returns._tokens: - array of token address of ERC20 tokens of CFMM

increaseCollateral(uint256).details: Deposit more collateral in loan identified by tokenId

returns.tokensHeld: - updated collateral token amounts backing loan

initialize(address,address[],uint8[],byt.details: Function to initialize state variables GammaPool, called usually from GammaPoolFactory contract right after GammaPool instantiation

params._cfmm: - address of CFMM GammaPool is for
params._data: - custom struct containing additional information used to verify the `_cfmm`
params._decimals: - decimals of CFMM tokens, indices must match _tokens[] array

liquidate(uint256,int256[],uint256[]).details: Function to liquidate a loan using its own collateral or depositing additional tokens. Seeks full liquidation

params.deltas: - amount tokens to trade to re-balance the collateral
params.fees: - fee on transfer for tokens[i]. Send empty array if no token in pool has fee on transfer or array of zeroes

returns.refund: - amounts from collateral tokens being refunded to liquidator

liquidateWithLP(uint256).details: Function to liquidate a loan using external LP tokens. Allows partial liquidation

returns.refund: - amounts from collateral tokens being refunded to liquidator

liquidationStrategy().details: Liquidation Strategy implementation contract for this GammaPool

loan(uint256).details: Get loan information for loan identified by tokenId

params._tokenId: - unique id of loan, used to look up loan in GammaPool

returns._loanData: - loan data struct (same as Loan + tokenId)

longStrategy().details: Long Strategy implementation contract for this GammaPool

protocolId().details: Protocol id of the implementation contract for this GammaPool

rebalanceCollateral(uint256,int256[]).details: Rebalance collateral amounts of loan identified by tokenId by purchasing or selling some of the collateral

params.deltas: - collateral amounts being bought or sold (>0 buy, <0 sell), index matches tokensHeld[] index. Only n-1 tokens can be traded

returns.tokensHeld: - updated collateral token amounts backing loan

repayLiquidity(uint256,uint256,uint256[].details: Repay liquidity debt of loan identified by tokenId, debt is repaid using available collateral in loan

params.fees: - fee on transfer for tokens[i]. Send empty array if no token in pool has fee on transfer or array of zeroes
params.liquidity: - liquidity debt being repaid, capped at actual liquidity owed. Can't repay more than you owe

returns.amounts: - collateral amounts consumed in repaying liquidity debt
returns.liquidityPaid: - liquidity amount that has been repaid

shortStrategy().details: Short Strategy implementation contract for this GammaPool

skim(address).details: Skim excess collateral tokens or CFMM LP tokens from GammaPool and send them to receiver (`to`) address

sync().details: Synchronize LP_TOKEN_BALANCE with actual CFMM LP tokens deposited in GammaPool

updatePool(uint256).details: Update pool liquidity debt and optinally also loan liquidity debt

params.tokenId: - (optional) unique ids identifying loan, pass zero to ignore this parameter

returns.loanLiquidityDebt: - updated liquidity debt amount of loan
returns.poolLiquidityDebt: - updated liquidity debt amount of pool

validateCFMM(address[],address,bytes).details: Check GammaPool for CFMM and tokens can be created with this implementation

params._cfmm: - address of CFMM GammaPool will be for
params._data: - custom struct containing additional information used to verify the `_cfmm`
params._tokens: - assumed tokens of CFMM, validate function should check CFMM is indeed for these tokens

returns._tokensOrdered: - tokens ordered to match the same order as in CFMM

withdrawNoPull(address).details: Withdraw CFMM LP token, by burning GS LP token, without doing a transferFrom transaction. Must have sent GS LP token first

params.to: - address of receiver of CFMM LP tokens

returns.assets: - quantity of CFMM LP tokens received for GS LP tokens

withdrawReserves(address).details: Withdraw reserve token quantities of CFMM (instead of CFMM LP tokens), by burning GS LP token

params.to: - address of receiver of reserve token quantities

returns.assets: - quantity of CFMM LP tokens representing reserve tokens withdrawn
returns.reserves: - quantity of reserve tokens withdrawn from CFMM and sent to receiver

getLatestPoolData().notice: Difference with getPoolData() is this struct is what PoolData would return if an update of the GammaPool were to occur at the current block

liquidate(uint256,int256[],uint256[]).notice: When calling this function and adding additional collateral it is assumed that you have sent the collateral first
